latestIgtvVideos.title: Beer garden outfit inspo🌈✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Today is the day for Scotland, we’re finally allowed out again 🥲 so here’s some ‘what I’d wear to a beer garden’ outfits. Can we all say a little prayer for the weather to change too- rain for a week isn’t fitting for my plans 🙃🤣

Let me know your favourite look and what you’ll be wearing out 🙌🏼

latestIgtvVideos.title: Spring dresses styled ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here’s a second episode of my styling series, it’s slightly longer (oops) but here I am showing you how to wear the same wrap dress in different ways! Also apologies for having my bra out for half the video, these things happen 🤣 
What’s your favourite way to wear it? OG or with a twist? ⬇️

latestIgtvVideos.title: Styling a ✨fedora✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here’s a highly requested video, like still amazes me people ask me questions about my outfits cause they’re sometimes weird af outfits 🤣 but this is how I’d style my black, pink and green fedora in casual and dressier ways! I’m sorry in advance how many times I say the words fedora, wee and erm- I’m working on saying erm less 🥴🤣 
Let me know in the comments below which of the fedoras and outfits you liked best and also what you’d like to see next! I have a few filmed but with things opening back up, if there’s something you have in your wardrobe you’re not sure on how to style, hmu and I can do a mini video on that. I’m thinking blazers, trainers, jeans, dresses etc ☺️ 
And if you make it to the end of the video thank you and congrats you deserve an award for watching 11 mins of me 🤣🙌🏼

*some items in the video were pr gifts

latestPosts.caption:
@frasers - what dundee has been needing for SO long 🥹🛍️✨ @overgatedundee 

guys when I say I felt emotional going to Frasers on Friday when it opened !!! we have been lacking on the high street here and finally we can get everything in one store 😭❤️ 

I’ve just shown a snippet of what’s in store but there’s SO many good brands like GANNI, Sweaty Betty & Never Fully Dressed in the clothes department, Trinny London, Charlotte Tilbury & Dior Beauty in the most amazing beauty hall and not to mention all the bags !! I couldn’t choose which to go for so help me out for me going into town again tomorrow 🤣🫶🏼

if you’ve not been yet, what are you most excited to shop? 😃⬇️🤍🛍️🫶🏼✨

I’ve been shopping at @fortkinnaird to find some cute new pieces for summer 😃☀️✈️🛍️✨ ad

i got some gorg bits for my next holiday from @hm @riverisland and @mango but which do we like best ?? 👇🏼

the difference between photo 7&8? nothing 😅🎭

latestPosts.caption:
glorious gardens afternoon tea at @vadundee lived up to its name 🥹👩🏼‍🌾🫜🪴🧁✨ @heritageportfolio 

so lucky to be invited back to v&a dundee to try their new menu in celebration of the garden futures exhibition🫶🏼 I just love the fact they incorporated edible flowers and garden ingredients in their menu, it was so delicious! I had the vegan version and Cameron the standard, my favourite part had to be the ‘cheese’ scone which tasted almost too good to be vegan😅

@vadundee always go above and beyond in their food menus and this is not one to miss ‼️
